&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Park House Surgery is a friendly, hard-working practice serving 8500 patients on the beautiful North Wales coast.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Two partners with excellent ANP, nursing and support staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engagement with a wide range of Enhanced Services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work-life balance is important to us&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We support flexible working patterns for parents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Newly qualified GPs welcome (mentoring/workload monitoring)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
