&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No ‘Out of Hours’ requirement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;EMIS Web&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Purpose built premises with a branch surgery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start date as soon as possible, but willing to wait for right candidate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
